OL,3,C9 facts you might not know about the
OL,4,Cnew super hospital in the West Midlands
OL,6,FThe Midland Metropolitan University
OL,7,FHospital is one of the biggest of its
OL,8,Fkind to open in the UK in the last
OL,9,Fdecade.
OL,11,FIt has been years in the making and
OL,12,Fwas expected to open in October 2019,
OL,13,Fbut was met with a series of delays
OL,14,Fdue to the pandemic, the collapse of a
OL,15,Fcontractor and shortage of
OL,16,Fconstruction workers.
OL,18,FBut the brand new super hospital
OL,19,Ffinally opened its doors on Sunday 6
OL,20,FOctober.
