OL,3,C9 facts you might not know about the
OL,4,Cnew super hospital in the West Midlands
OL,6,FHere are some facts you might not yet
OL,7,Fknow about the Midland Metropolitan
OL,8,FUniversity Hospital.
OL,10,F1. The hospital spans an area
OL,11,Fequivalent to 22 football pitches,
OL,12,Fwith more than 4,000 rooms across 11
OL,13,Ffloors.
OL,15,F2. There is also 28,000 metres of
OL,16,Fplasterboard used in the hospital.
OL,17,FThat is enough to fill 160 lorries.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/5
