OL,3,C9 facts you might not know about the
OL,4,Cnew super hospital in the West Midlands
OL,6,F3. Robots are being used onsite to
OL,7,Fhelp with heavy-lifting. Twelve
OL,8,Fautomated guided vehicles (AGVs) are
OL,9,Fworking away behind the scenes,
OL,10,Ftransporting heavy things like laundry
OL,11,Fand rubbish across the 11 floors.
OL,13,F4. The hospital has more than 30
OL,14,Fdifferent colour schemes, which has
OL,15,Fused more than 18,340 litres of paint.
OL,17,F5. There are 633 CCTV cameras fitted
OL,18,Facross the whole site.
