OL,3,C9 facts you might not know about the
OL,4,Cnew super hospital in the West Midlands
OL,6,F6. The hospital uses 800km of voltage
OL,7,Fcables, which could take you from the
OL,8,FSandwell to Scotland and back again.
OL,10,F7. There will be a winter garden and
OL,11,Foutdoor spaces which are designed to
OL,12,Fhelp patients stay active.
OL,14,F8. A two-way talk system is in place,
OL,15,Fwhich will mean patients can directly
OL,16,Fconnect with nurses in emergencies.
OL,17,FThis will be a more convenient and
OL,18,Feffective replacement of old 'buzzer'
OL,19,Fdevices.
